{"id":1209,"date":"2024-08-03T20:24:06","date_gmt":"2024-08-03T20:24:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1209"},"modified":"2024-08-03T20:24:06","modified_gmt":"2024-08-03T20:24:06","slug":"mission-020","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-020\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #020: Exp. Millionaire"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #020: Exp. Millionaire<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Fallshore City, Mission HQ 1F &#8211; Lady near fridge<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Become Pokemon Champion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Earn 1,000,000 EXP in one day<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td>\n        <u>Item<\/u>: <strong>2 Lucky Eggs<\/strong><br \/>\n        <u>Service<\/u>: Lucky Egg Upgrades\n      <\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>In the Fallshore Mission HQ, a well-dressed lady would like you to earn at least 1 million EXP in one day. If you manage to complete this task, you\u2019ll get 2 Lucky Eggs and the ability to upgrade the Lucky Egg multiplier.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>The Mission HQ is on the west side of Fallshore City just north of the Marketplace.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/020\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-fallshore-city-mission-hq.jpg\" alt=\"The Fallshore City Mission HQ \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Fallshore City Mission HQ<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>On the first floor of the building, there\u2019s a lady in the kitchen with a mission for you.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/020\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-lady-in-the-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"The lady in the kitchen \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The lady in the kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll need to earn at least 1,000,000 EXP in a single day.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<p>You can challenge the Elite Four again, and this will give a lot of EXP as they\u2019re all high-level Pok\u00e9mon. <\/p>\n<p>Repeatable battles such as those at the Dresco Battle House and the Seaport City Camomons House would also be good.<\/p>\n<p>Or Raid Dens are also a good source of EXP, and you can challenge each of the 32 Dens in Borrius at least once daily.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/020\/03-pokemon-unbound-search-for-a-metapod.jpg\" alt=\"Search for a Metapod \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Search for a Metapod<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Tip:<\/strong> Having a Lucky Egg equipped on your Pok\u00e9mon while they do any of these battles will also accelerate this process.\n<\/div>\n<p>For completing the mission, you\u2019ll receive 2 Lucky Eggs to put on more Pok\u00e9mon, as well as the ability to upgrade the EXP multiplier effect.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Tip:<\/strong> To upgrade the Lucky Egg fully to Lv.10, you\u2019ll need 28 Big Pearls and 9 Pearl Strings.\n<\/div>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1210,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1209","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1209","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1210"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1209"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1209"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}